{"tid":1672424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸委會主委：管神棍唔該收皮啦！","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:59:31.000Z","uid":247122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2042314d9e1c7c7f19b6d7315e65ecbc10b215","tid":1672424,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"涉在台灣殺女友疑犯陳同佳昨（23日）出獄，港府稱其願赴台投案，陸委會派檢警赴港押人卻遭拒，台港角力，讓國民黨找到着力點，痛批蔡政府在陳同佳案髮夾彎，丟失主權；立法院內政委員會今變更議程，增列邀請司法院、內政部、陸委會等針對「目前我國與香港地區犯罪及追訴概況」進行專題報告。內政委員會召委林為洲表示，該案是首例，也是特例，惟有研商對策，才能達到共同打擊犯罪的目的。至於香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴擔心怕受到政治力影響，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陸委會主委陳明通則表示，如果管浩鳴有心為受害港女伸張正義，就讓陳同佳來台受審，請你少說兩句話。有港媒今天欲訪問管浩鳴被拒絕，「我想今天不再多説話，給我們一點時間」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191024/60188502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60188502&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=25353d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191024%2F60188502&h=c698941d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191024/60188502</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191024/large/1571884784_0697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191024%2Flarge%2F1571884784_0697.jpg&h=4a416683&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}